<title>ạkẖtbrt ḥbk dẖlk ạlḥb ạlfryd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạkẖtbrt ḥbk dẖlk ạlḥb ạlfryd
 wʿrft km ykwn lys ḥb llkẖlwd
 ạldẖy qd ạḥtwạny wạḥtwy̱ kl ʿnyd
 ạ̹lạ ḥbk ạ̹lhy dạỷmaⁿạ bạqiⁿ wṭyd

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: hkdẖạ ạ̉ḥbbtny yạ lḥbk ạlʿjyb
   ṣạr ḥbk kẖlạṣy wslạmy fy ạlḥyạh
   qd ʿlạ fwq ạlsdwd wtjly̱ fy ạlṣlyb
   wbdẖạt ạlḥb ạ̉dnw byqyniⁿ fy ạlṣlạh

[V2]
 2- ạkẖtbrt ḥbk fy ậlạmy wạlftwr
 fwq ḍʿfy tʿlw by ạ̉nt tjbr ạlkswr
 km blmsẗ tdạwy kl sqm wgẖrwr
 fyfyḍ ạlqlb mʿk bạlslạm wạlsrwr</lyrics>
</song>